[preface]
== Preface by Mybrid Wonderful

Welcome to the wonderful world of words!

Welcome to New Democracy that is of the people, by the people, and for the people, but otherwise everything else is new!

This book is intended for everyone on planet Earth. This is not an academic text at the university level. It is a conversation suitable for YouTube video scripts for those who prefer video to reading. 

I believe happy people create happy environments where unhappy people cannot. Therefore this book has unrelated art, cooking recipes and other goodies to make it shiny! 

You can freely copy this book. It is in the public domain. The hope is as many people as possible rewrite, sell, and make videos promoting New Democracy. 

Therefore I gave this book a brand, "Irreni World Scale". This way when there exits multitudes of New Democracy books then you can find this one by searching on Irreni.

You can find Irreni online at: https://irreni.social/.

The purpose of New Democracy is to address and solve all the problems of existing Democracy, hereafter referred to as Old Democracy.

New Democracy is a huge umbrella of ideas and you can choose to engage as much or as little as suits you.



